overcome his upbringing.

256
00:15:34.935 --> 00:15:36.269
you know...

257
00:15:36.293 --> 00:15:38.748
-[speaking indistinctly]
<i>-Gangs. drugs.</i>

258
00:15:38.772 --> 00:15:40.063
<i>And he overdosed.</i>

259
00:15:40.999 --> 00:15:44.653
